name: Face Generation
description:
Honored to collaborate with @Brutalisti! The visuals in this piece were inspired by  his dance career. Straight from the soul... The music inspires the dance, motion, movement, and a deep desire for creativity. I hope you enjoy it...

Musicians: Andy Sells-drums, Jimmy James-guitar samples, Marc Fendel-synth bass

Recorded and Mixed in Seattle, Washington 9/2021
